Package Medicine

Class MedicineData

java.lang.Object
Medicine.MedicineData
public class MedicineData extends Object
The MedicineData class provides methods to manage the data of medicines stored in a CSV file. It allows fetching, adding, updating, and removing medicine records. It also provides functionality to check the stock levels of medicines.
